				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I am shocked to find that Jupiter and Saturn are visible to the naked eye. As to the realism of massive tidal effects when Saturn and Jupiter were suddenly removed I just don&#8217;t know &#8211; Jupiter is 1% the mass of the sun so I suspect it&#8217;s absence would radically upset earth&#8217;s stable orbit.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

